messages.text: You trying to link?
Slow down lol, we just started talking. What's ur fave travel spot?

Haha fair enough, just thought I’d shoot my shot. Favorite travel spot’s gotta be Chicago—close enough for a quick trip, dope food, and the lakefront’s unreal. What about you, where’s your go-to getaway?
Chicago’s cool, love the vibe there. Bali’s my go-to, obviously. Ur fave food spot?

Bali, damn, that’s next level. I’ve never been, but it’s on the list now. For food, there’s this pizza joint in Columbus called Mikey’s Late Night Slice—greasy, cheap, and hits every time. What’s your favorite spot to eat, Bali or wherever? And hey, if you’re ever around Columbus, we should grab a slice together.
Mikey's sounds dope, love greasy pizza. Bali street food’s my jam. And nah, I don’t meet up from here, but check my OF if u wanna connect more. What's ur go-to topping?

Bali street food sounds fire, I’d be all over that. As for pizza, I’m a pepperoni guy—classic, never fails. So about the OF, what kinda stuff you got on there? I’m curious, but not gonna lie, I was hoping to meet up for real. If that’s off the table, just wanna know what I’m signing up for.
Pepperoni’s solid, can’t go wrong. Check my OF, u’ll see what’s up there.
Cool, I’ll take a peek at your OF to see what’s good. How much does it run, by the way? Still kinda bummed we can’t grab a bite or something in person, but I’ll check it out for now.
Damn what I would do to you
Haha, u got some wild thoughts? Where u from?
Hell yeah, I got some wild thoughts. I’m from Manhattan, born and raised. How about you, where you at?
Nice, I'm visiting Manhattan this week for work. U around?

No kidding, that’s perfect timing. Yeah, I’m around. What part of Manhattan you staying in? Maybe we can grab a drink or something. Gotta make sure you’re real first though, haha. Too many fakes out here on IG.
Haha, maybe! I barely know u tho. What’s ur vibe like?

Fair enough. I’m a pretty laid-back guy, work as a sales rep so I’m good at talking to people, cracking a joke or two. I like to keep things chill, maybe hit up a cool bar or just walk around the city. Not into games or wasting time though. So, what’s your deal? You into meeting up or just here to chat?
I’m chill too, love a good vibe. But I don’t meet up from IG, babe. If u wanna get closer, my OF is where I’m more open. What’s ur go-to spot in the city?

Ah, got it. OF, huh? What kinda stuff you got on there? I’m curious. As for my go-to spot, I’m big on this little bar in the East Village called Please Don’t Tell. Hidden vibe, killer drinks. You’d probably dig it if you ever change your mind about meeting up.
Haha, u gotta check my OF to see. That bar sounds dope tho!
Alright, fair play. How much does it run to check out your OF? I might take a peek. And yeah, that bar’s a gem—maybe one day I’ll convince ya to swing by for a drink, haha.
Let's get drinks sometime

haha maybe! i barely know u tho  
what’s ur fave spot to chill?
Fair enough, I get it. Gotta know me a bit first. I like this low-key bar in Astoria called The Shady Lady—good vibes, strong drinks. What about you, where do you usually hang out?

nice, sounds chill! i’m usually just vibin in Bali spots.  
u ever been out here?

Bali, huh? Nah, never made it out there. I’m more of a local guy—stick to Queens or Manhattan mostly. You’re actually in Bali right now? Gotta say, I’m a little skeptical you’re not just a bot or something with a profile like yours. Prove me wrong, haha. You down to meet up if you’re ever in NYC?
Wait you're really in Charlotte?
Yup, just visiting for a bit. U from here?
Yeah, born and raised. What part of town are you staying in? Maybe I could show you around if you’re up for it.
Slow down lol, we just started talking. What’s ur fave spot in Charlotte?
Haha, fair enough. I’d say my favorite spot is Freedom Park. It’s chill, great for a walk or just to relax. What about you, got any places you’ve liked so far while you’re here?
Haven’t explored much yet tbh. Freedom Park sounds cool tho. What else u into?

I’m into checking out local breweries, catching live music when I can, and just kicking back with friends. Work keeps me busy with marketing stuff, but I try to balance it out. What about you, what do you like to do for fun?
Love dancing, yoga, and traveling. Always up for an adventure. U into music too?

Yeah, I’m definitely into music. Love catching live shows when I can—rock, indie, whatever’s got a good vibe. Do you dance at clubs or more like freestyle stuff? Maybe we could hit up a spot with some good tunes while you’re in town.
Haha, ur cute but idk about meeting yet. I do freestyle mostly. Favorite band?

Thanks, haha. No pressure on meeting up, just thought I’d throw it out there. Freestyle dancing sounds cool—bet you’ve got some moves. Favorite band’s gotta be The Black Keys. What about you, who’re you into?
Black Keys are solid! I’m into Tame Impala. Got that chill vibe. U dance too?

Tame Impala’s awesome, love their vibe. Nah, I’m not much of a dancer myself—more of a head-nodder at shows, haha. I’d probably just watch you steal the spotlight. So, you been to any cool concerts lately?

messages.text: Hi there
Heyy, how’s it going? Where u from?
Hey, I’m doing good, thanks. I’m from Chicago. How about you? Gotta say, I’m a little curious if you’re even real haha—lots of bots out here.
Heyy, I’m from Minnesota but living in Bali. Totally real, no bot here lol. U from Chicago originally?
Nice, Bali sounds amazing. Yeah, born and raised in Chicago. So, what brought you all the way to Bali? And haha, good to know you’re real—got any proof, like a pic with a goofy face or something? 😉
Bali’s a vibe, moved for the freedom and inspo. Sorry, no pics here babe. If u wanna get closer, my OF is where I’m more open tbh. What do u do in Chicago?

Fair enough, Bali does seem like the ultimate escape. I’m a teacher here in Chicago, just shaping young minds one day at a time. So, about your OF—what kind of stuff do you post on there? I’m curious, but not gonna lie, I’m not super into paying for content unless I know it’s worth it.
Heyy, I get it. It’s all on my OF babe. Worth checking if ur curious. How’s teaching going for u?

Teaching’s good, keeps me busy and on my toes. I’m still kinda curious, though—can you give me a hint about what’s on your OF? Like, is it just pics or something more? I’m not trying to be cheap, just wanna know what I’m signing up for. Also, how much does it cost?
Heyy
Heyy, how’s it going? Where u from?
Heyy, I'm doing good, just chilling after a long shift. I'm from Detroit, born and raised. How about you, where you from?
Heyy, glad ur chilling. I’m from Minnesota, but in Bali now. U always in Detroit?

Bali, damn, that sounds exotic. Yeah, I’m still in Detroit, been here my whole life. Work as a nurse, so I’m pretty tied down with shifts at the hospital. Ever think about coming back stateside, or you just living the island life now? I’d love to meet up if you’re ever around.
Bali’s a vibe, tbh. Ur cute, but idk about meeting yet lol. What’s ur fave thing about Detroit?

Haha, thanks, I appreciate that. Detroit’s got a grit to it, you know? My favorite thing’s gotta be the history—Motown, the auto industry, all that. Plus, the people here got heart. I get not wanting to meet up right away, no pressure. Just saying, I’d be down to grab a coffee or something if you’re ever around. What’s keeping you in Bali? You got a gig out there or just soaking up the sun?
Detroit’s history sounds dope. I’m in Bali for the vibes and freedom, babe. Can’t meet up, but if u wanna get to know me better, my OF is where I’m more open. What do u do for fun there?

Bali vibes and freedom sound nice, I ain’t gonna lie. As for fun, I usually just kick back with some buddies, hit up a local bar, or catch a Lions game when I ain’t working crazy hours at the hospital. About that OF though—what’s on there? I’m curious, but I gotta be real, I’m trying to figure out if you’re even legit or just playing me here. lol. Lay it out for me.
Hey, I get it. My OF’s got the real me, babe. Check it out if u wanna see more. What’s ur go-to bar in Detroit?

Alright, I’ll think about checking out your OF, just to see what’s up. Gotta admit, I’m still a bit skeptical, but I’m curious. My go-to bar in Detroit is this spot called Cliff Bell’s—old-school jazz vibe, real chill. What’s the deal with your OF, though? Like, how much does it cost to get a peek at the “real you”? If it’s worth it, I might take a look.
You're really pretty
Thanks babe! Where u from?
Thanks for the reply. I'm from Detroit. Gotta ask though, are you for real? I’ve run into a few bots on here, haha. Where you from?
Haha no bot here! I’m from Minnesota, just visiting Detroit. U from here?
Yeah, born and raised in Detroit. Own a small business here too. Since you’re in town, wanna grab a drink or something? I’d love to meet up and see if we vibe in person.
Haha maybe! I barely know u tho. Tell me more about urself first.

Fair enough. I’m 40, been running my own business here in Detroit for about a decade now—kinda my pride and joy. I’m into cars, good food, and just chilling with friends when I’m not working. Pretty laid-back guy overall. What about you? And hey, I get wanting to know me better, but I’d rather chat over a coffee or drink if you’re up for it. No pressure though.
Sounds cool! I’m into art and travel. Tell me bout ur fave car?

Nice, art and travel are a dope combo. My favorite car’s gotta be a classic—1969 Chevy Camaro. Something about that muscle and style just gets me. I’ve been fixing one up in my spare time. What kind of art you into? And hey, if you’re still around Detroit, I’d love to show you around or grab that drink. Lemme know if you’re down.
That Camaro sounds hot! I’m into abstract art mostly. And hey, I’m way more fun over there tbh, that’s what my OF is for babe. So, what’s ur fave spot in Detroit?

Abstract art, huh? That’s cool, I like stuff that makes you think. As for my fave spot in Detroit, gotta be the riverfront—great views, chill vibes, good for a walk or just to hang. So, about this OF thing… what’s on there exactly? I’m curious, but not gonna lie, I was hoping to meet up in person. You still around Detroit?
Riverfront sounds dope! All the good stuff is on my OF babe. 😉

Haha, alright, I get the hint. How much does it cost to check out your OF? I’m still more into meeting up in person though, so if you’re still in Detroit, lemme know. I’m not gonna push too hard on that, just thought it’d be cool to hang.
Damn what I would do to you
Haha, oh really? What’s on ur mind, babe?
Haha, well, let’s just say I’ve got some ideas that might make us both smile. What’s a gorgeous woman like you doing on here anyway? Gotta admit, I’m half wondering if you’re even real. 😏
Lol, I’m real, trust me. Just here chillin and chatting. Where u from?

Good to hear, I’ll believe it when I see it though. I’m from San Diego, just kicking back after a long day of teaching. How about you, where you at? Maybe we could grab a drink sometime if you’re close. 😎
Slow down lol, we just started talking. Tell me more about urself first.

Fair enough, haha. I’m 54, been teaching high school history for a while now down here in San Diego. I’m into hiking, hitting the beach, and just enjoying life outside the classroom. Not gonna lie, I’m a bit of a flirt when I meet someone as stunning as you. So, what’s your story? You’ve got me curious. 😉
Haha, thanks babe. I’m just livin life, lovin art and travel. What’s ur fave hike?

Nice, art and travel are a solid combo. My favorite hike’s gotta be Torrey Pines right here in San Diego—killer ocean views and just the right amount of challenge. You ever been out this way? I’d love to show you the trails sometime, maybe grab a bite after. What do you think? 😏
Sounds cool, but subscribe to my OF and maybe we can talk about it.
Haha, alright, I’ll bite. What’s on your OF? Gotta know what I’m signing up for before I pull the trigger. 😉
Subscribe and find out, babe. Promise it’s worth it. 😏
Tempting, but I’m old school—I like to know what I’m getting into. How much does it cost to check out? Might take a peek if the price is right. 😎
